{
  "stem": "13623.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Some of the group that we were still together, including the rabbi from our-- from our town went to one or the other, either Harzungen or Ellrich.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A few of us were still left in Dora.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was one of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- they may have had a-- a method of selecting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just-- we were standing on-- on Zahlappell, and they would call prisoner number so-and-so report to a certain spot, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had a group they would send out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know where they were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they wound up, we found out later on, on little satellite camps that belonged to Dora.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some of these people were working in the tunnel on the opposite side that we entered from the Dora side.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were working with these jackhammers, digging, where they were telling me that at the end of the day, they would be all white from the dust of the stone from by digging with that vibration thing.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I'm still-- I'm still in Dora.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'm still working in that kommando that we were digging these irrigation ditches.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In this case, it was just a matter of luck how you were assigned to different work details.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They took me off from that work detail.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they put me in to work in a-- in a nursery.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I want to tell you this camp had maybe 20,000 inmates.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had-- there was a jail in the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were-- most-- a lot of people worked in the tunnel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "People worked on the railroad-- on the railroad siding.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
